tspan.tspan: 200408: RNAseAlert kit: test 04 - Cas13 RNAse activity
Cas13 protein 10x; 5ul of stock Cas13 (2mg/ml) diluted by adding 153ul of strorage buffer (SB)
Cas13 protein 50x; 5ul of stock Cas13 (2mg/ml) diluted by adding 76.5ul of strorage buffer (SB)
Storage buffer for Cas13 (Kellner at al, NM, 2019)
substrate one tube + 15ul 10x buffer (kit) top up to 150ul with nuclease free water (Josie)
dilute 10x for the reaction to obtain 1E5/ul
Add 5ul of substrate to the plate, then add 45ul of reaction to it.
Volumes in ul per well. For 4 rplicates multiply by 4 then by 1.15
Working in quadruplicates, pipet the same reaction in squares to achieve an even variances.
Incubate at 37°C (in Varioscan) and measure for up to one hour (e.g. 24min).
Measure fluorescence every 2min, ex/em 490/520nm, read each well for 100ms with 10ul delay.
